1. Oni *šalju* pisma svojim prijateljima. (They send letters to their friends.)
2. Ja *šaljem* mejlove svakodnevno. (I send emails every day.)
3. Mi *šaljemo* pakete poštom. (We send packages by mail.)
4. Ti *šalješ* poruke putem mobilnog telefona. (You send messages via your mobile phone.)
5. On *šalje* cveće svojoj devojci. (He sends flowers to his girlfriend.)
6. Ona *šalje* molbu za posao. (She sends a job application.)
7. Njih dvojica *šalju* pozdrave rođacima. (The two of them send greetings to their relatives.)
8. Vi *šaljete* novac u inostranstvo. (You send money abroad.)
9. Svi *šalju* misli i molitve povređenima. (Everyone sends thoughts and prayers to the injured.)
10. Učenici *šalju* domaće zadatke na mejl profesoru. (Students send homework to their teacher via email.)